request.description:
Deeper check than `/v1/health` — also pings Postgres. Use as the Kubernetes readiness probe upstream of any deploy of your integration.

**No auth required.**

**Response (200):**
```json
{
  "status": "ok",
  "checks": { "database": "ok" }
}
```

Returns 200 even if a check fails (with `status: degraded`); inspect `checks` for detail.
